                                <h4><strong>Confidentiality and Security</strong></h4>
                                <p class="text-justify">The confidentiality and security of your personal information is as important to us as is to you. We have invested resources into protecting and safekeeping your personal data. We take all steps to keep your information safe with us, regardless of where the information is stored or transferred. </p>
                                <h4><strong>Study in India Digital Privacy Policy</strong></h4>
                                <p class="text-justify">We adhere to the Data Protection Act and / or any other applicable laws, when collecting, using or dealing with any information provided by you. We only collect your personal information when you communicate or register with us, and in cases where you could visit our digital platforms.</p>
                                <p class="text-justify">We collect your personal information for the following purposes:</p>
