                                <p class="text-justify">However, we shall not share information in the following cases: </p>
                                <ul class="privacyUL">
                                    <li>There is reason to suspect unlawful activity of a serious nature.</li>
                                    <li>There is a chance of revealing evaluative information in connection with our commercial processes.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p class="text-justify">You have the following rights to your personal information that we hold:</p>
                                <ul class="privacyUL">
                                    <li>We will remove any / all data which we may have taken by mistake or do not require, on your request. </li>
                                    <li>A right to restrict processing information will be enabled as soon as you seek to update or revise any personal information shared with us.</li>
                                    <li>You can withdraw your consent for processing any information shared by you. </li>
                                    <li>You can also object to processing your information. </li>
                                    <li>We do not automate all of our processing activities and profiling, but we do warn you in case of one. </li>
                                    <li>You can request access to information shared by you anytime.</li>
